## Summary

The PostCard system is currently designed for basic interactions (like, comment, bookmark, repost) with no emoji or reaction system in place. The ActionBar component provides the UI framework, but action handlers are currently not wired in HomeFeedScreen (they navigate to detail screens instead). The social API has a `likeJournal` endpoint but no method for emoji reactions or reaction management. The feed data includes basic reaction counts but no emoji reaction data structures.
